{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"edf7ddb82d","title":"毛泽东对上海市革委会的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4a8686da63","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"edf7ddb82d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"56a499f88d","name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"47aebae637","type":"title","text":"对上海市革委会的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"edf7ddb82d"},{"id":"a0b19d5668","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"edf7ddb82d"},{"id":"0830ec7183","type":"paragraph","text":"一、这次双方都有经验，这股风不会刮得很大，我们要遵守“八条”，解放军得遵守“十条”。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"edf7ddb82d"},{"id":"effc64885d","type":"paragraph","text":"二、解放十几年来，我们脱离群众是很厉害的。青联、妇联、团中央都是空架子。我们的要求是不脱产，既当官，又当老百姓。假如不当老百姓，有什么办法呢？一个月里当一个星期的官，三个星期的老百姓。假如不当老百姓，工人运动的领袖，这样下去就可能变。这个是大方向问题。办法是否好，同志们可以提出来。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"edf7ddb82d"}],"page":{"id":"2a51974d5c","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"edf7ddb82d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}